data.description: Tucked into a quiet cul-de-sac, this fabulous tri-level floor plan is one of 16 homes in the Spring Tree Neighborhood. There are soaring ceilings & wood look flooring in the main entry & kitchen. You will love the island kitchen with slab granite, tile backsplash, walk in pantry, island sink, lots of beautiful cabinetry. Down a short few steps to a spacious fam room w/gas fireplace & room for multiple furniture arrangements. Separate formal dining room, lovely main floor powder room. Updated baths. All bedrooms including primary suite are upstairs along with full bath. Large fully fenced yard with 2 level rebuilt & painted decks & 2 good sized side yards. 3 car garage is huge! Great location just minutes to Hwy 16, Costco & other shopping.
